{"tid":1366798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［劉細良提醒］依家要鬥智！唔係鬥勇！","createTime":"2019-07-26T05:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:01:33.000Z","uid":61520,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22d2ef647e79e14716acbe78626a5d76676bc6da","tid":1366798,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"細良727-特備講話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">重點：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">（1）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反警黑</span></span>係自69以來，我地前所未有既道德高度，正常有智慧既香港人都唔會唔支持。所以！依家只需<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬥智</span></span>鬥冷靜，唔係鬥勇鬥人多哂馬，更加<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係去復仇</span></span>開拖。我地就係要話俾所有人聽，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地未驚過</span></span>，亦唔會似黑幫咁低端鬥暴力。遊行照去，反警黑為口號！ <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 仲未對現到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">（2）</span></span><br />\n既然有道德高地，我地有大把方法對付敵人。拆大公報招牌、反對丁申等就係好例子，相關政府部門會暗中支援呢類行動。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民間</span></span>可組織<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">調查委員會</span></span>自己調查，請來高公信力人物，驚方愈避就愈黑，亦相信會有人出尼做污點證人。總之，我地自己發揮創意，用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法治方式抗爭</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">（3）</span></span><br />\n政府同建制內部已是人人自危，因為涉及重大道德危機。有智商既政府人員其實都好想同林奠割蓆。下一步就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爭取公務員罷工或按章工作</span></span>。林奠政權最大支撐就係公務員，公務員都割蓆林奠就輸！"},{"pid":"b8407bc3f9463aa4ae4254716a34a048d9d10bc0","tid":1366798,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2405f16df1a3b0fb459cad026aded91a24fe4b57","tid":1366798,"uid":284559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"推"}]}